&lt;li>&lt;code>server_addr&lt;/code> &lt;em>String&lt;/em>: IP address of interface and port to bind web server (e.g. 0.0.0.0:8080 for all)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>public_server_url&lt;/code> &lt;em>String&lt;/em> (optional): Public base URL of the server (e.g. &lt;code>https://bbox.example.com/&lt;/code>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>loglevel&lt;/code> &lt;em>Loglevel&lt;/em> (optional): Log level (Default: info)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>tls_cert&lt;/code> &lt;em>String&lt;/em> (optional)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>tls_key&lt;/code> &lt;em>String&lt;/em> (optional)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>cors&lt;/code> &lt;a href="#cors" >Cors&lt;/a> (optional)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
